author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-‍The9 Limited Announces Receipt Of Nasdaq Notice Of Deficiency​
text:
April 9, 2018 / 9:04 AM / Updated 39 minutes ago BRIEF-‍The9 Limited Announces Receipt Of Nasdaq Notice Of Deficiency​ Reuters Staff 
April 9 (Reuters) - The9 Ltd: 
* ‍THE9 LIMITED ANNOUNCES RECEIPT OF NASDAQ NOTICE OF DEFICIENCY​ 
* LOOKING INTO VARIOUS OPTIONS AVAILABLE TO REGAIN COMPLIANCE AND MAINTAIN ITS CONTINUED LISTING ON NASDAQ GLOBAL MARKET​ 
* ‍CONSIDERING OTHER OPTIONS, INCLUDING A POTENTIAL TRANSFER OF ITS LISTING OF SECURITIES TO NASDAQ CAPITAL MARKET​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
